OL,4,CFarming in Wales: Deaths on farms more
OL,5,Cthan double in a year
OL,6, The number of fatal farming accidents
OL,7, in Wales more than doubled last year,
OL,8, according to official figures.
OL,10,FA report by the Health and Safety
OL,11,FExecutive (HSE) showed there were seven
OL,12,Fdeaths in 2020-21, compared with three
OL,13,Fin 2019-20.
OL,15,FFarmer Alun Hopkins, 80, said he would
OL,16,Ftake more care after he broke his ankle
OL,17,Fand spent two days in hospital when he
OL,18,Fwas charged by a cow in February.
OL,20,FThe HSE called it "disappointing" and
OL,21,Furged farmers to call out bad practise.
